headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Smuggler
content:
Ever been told the sky is the limit? Well, not anymore. It’s time to expand your criminal empire in the only direction left to go: straight up.

Vast and customizable Hangar properties are the center for your new smuggling ring; stock it with a fleet of lovingly personalized aircraft, take to the skies, and don’t come down until every cubic foot of Los Santos airspace has been brought under the control of a tax-exempt Air-Freight Business stretching from sea to shining sea.
